The '''Lake Fire''' was a wildfire that burned in the [[San Bernardino National Forest]]. The fire started on June 17, 2015 and burned over 31,359 acres before it was fully contained on July 21, 2015.<ref>{{cite press release |url=http://inciweb.nwcg.gov/incident/4302/ |title=News Release: Lake Fire|publisher=USDA Forest Service |date=2014-06-26 |accessdate=2015-06-26 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Hamilton |first=Matt |url=http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-wildfire-san-bernardino-mountains-grows-winds-shift-20150624-story.html |title=Wildfire in San Bernardino Mountains grows to nearly 21,000 acres after winds shift |work=Los Angeles Times |date=2015-06-25 |accessdate=2015-06-25 }}</ref>

